name: Empowered Waifu #7
description:
"We Can Do It." There is nothing in this world that these waifus can't do for you.

Deana fell for your persistence. She watched you in your hard times, and how you it only made you stronger. She watched you learning to overcome your weakness. And day by day, Deana's love became nothing but resoluteness. "I'll stand by this man," she said to herself.
